  .tab-content
    #brand_development.tab-pane.active(role='tabpanel')
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Branding & Visual Identity
          p We offer a range of creative solutions including naming, brand positioning and visual identity design.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Logo & Wordmark Design
          p Your logo or wordmark is the core of your brand identity. Our team of designers create appealing logos that will communicate the proper brand image and message to your clients.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Typographic Treatments
          p A great brand identity requires an equally strong family of fonts that work well across all print and digital media.
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Colour Palette
          p A strategically selected colour palette ties all your marketing materials together. We will help you select the proper colour palette for your firm.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Visual Language
          p The visual language and elements you use including photography, iconography, and other graphic elements define your brand voice. We can help you get it right.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Brand Guidelines
          p Your brand guidelines define the use of your brand elements. Our design team can help you create a unified brand message across all channels and media.
    #marketing.tab-pane(role='tabpanel')
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Marketing Strategy
          p Our team of strategists can help you identify your ideal types of clients and define the proper marketing tactics to reach them.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Lead Generation
          p Baustein can create the proper print, social, and email marketing campaigns to reach your target audiences and build your client base.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Video Marketing
          p Research shows that integrating video into your marketing activities can help increase client acquisition rates. We offer a complete video solution from concept development, to filming, post-production, and marketing.     
    #design.tab-pane(role='tabpanel')  
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Marketing Collateral
          p Properly designed marketing collateral will properly communicate your firm’s value and attract the right types of clients.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Corporate Brochures
          p Our team can design and manage the print production of corporate and fund brochures that will appeal to your clients.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Presentations
          p Talk to us if you need professional presentations created to pitch funds or different investment scenarious to your clients.
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Factsheets
          p We can help you communicate your fund information in a visually appealing way.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Investor Reports
          p Good design can help you effectively communicate to investors.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Annual Reports
          p Our design team can help tell your story with print, interactive, and web based annual reports.
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Newsletters
          p Want to stay in touch with your clients? We can design the right newsletter concept for your firm and help manage the delivery to your target audiences.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Print Ads
          p Baustein can design print ad campaigns to target channel partners and investors.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Infographics
          p Communicate important information and strategies to your clients with visually appealing infographics.
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Photography
          p Baustein’s photography solutions can cover all your requirements from stock images to custom created photography.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Video
          p Baustein provides a complete video design, filming, editing, production, and delivery solution that can enhance communication with your clients.
    #websites.tab-pane(role='tabpanel')
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Website Design & Build
          p Our modern, responsive, mobile friendly websites are designed to communicate your information and engage your clients across all devices.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 SEO
          p Our team will define the proper search engine optimisation program to increase your visibility in the most popular search engines.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 SEM
          p When you want to generate new client leads, our team can create the proper online advertising campaigns to reach your target audiences as they use search.
